quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  18,84,"Zvirokwazvo, takamudzika panyika uye tikamupa zvinhu zvese"
  18,85,Naizvozvo akatevera nzira
  18,86,"Kusvikira asvika kwainyura zuva (kumadokero), akariwana richinyura muchitubu chenhope nhema yaipisa, uye akawana pedyo pacho (chitubu) pane vanhu. Tikati (Allah): “Iwe Dhul- Qarnain! Unokwanisa kuvaranga kana kuvabata zvakanaka.”"
  18,87,"Akati (Dhul-Qarnain): “Uyo anoita mabasa akaipa, tichamuranga, uye achadzoswa kuna Tenzi vake avo vachamuranga nemurango wakaomarara (Gehena).”"
  18,88,"“Uye uyo achatenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah), uye oita mabasa akanaka, achawana mubairo wakanaka (Paradhiso), uye achataura naye (Dhul-Qarnain) mashoko akanaka.”"
  18,89,Naizvozvo akatevera (imwe) nzira
  18,90,"Kusvika asvika kunzvimbo yaibudira zuva (kumabvazuva), akariwana richibudira kune vanhu vatisina kupa bvute kuzuva"
  18,91,"Zvakaitika kudaro! Zvirokwazvo, taiziva zvese maererano naye (Dhul-Qarnain)"
  18,92,Naizvozvo akatevera (imwe) nzira
  18,93,"Kusvika asvika pakati pemakomo maviri, akawana pedyo nawo (makomo) vanhu vakanga vari pedyo kusanzwa kana shoko"
  18,94,"Vakati: “Iwe Dhul-Qarnain! Zvirokwazvo, vana Ya’jooj naMa’jooj (Gog naMagog) vari kukonzeresa panyika. Naizvozvo tingakupe matano here kuti uvake mudhuri pakati pedu navo?”"
  18,95,"Akati: “Zvandakatsigiswa naTenzi vangu zvirinani. Naizvozvo ndibetserei nesimba (varume) kuti ndimise mudhuri pakati penyu navo.”"
  18,96,"“Ndipei zvidimbu zvesimbi.” Naizvozvo paakazadza mpata pakati pemakomo maviri, akati: “Furidzai.” Naizvozvo paakazviita kunge moto akati: “Ndipei mhangura yakanyunguduka ndidire pamusoro pazvo.”"
  18,97,Naizvozvo (vana Gog naMagog) vakatadza kuukwira (mudhuri) nepamusoro kana kuuchera kusvika kuseri